<img src=http://homex.coolconnect.com/member3/Tiejinnie/images/Avatar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> I'm L50,<br>
<br>
an L50 SB Perfed me for 1071dmg standing [AF98 armor 20% Bonus, 100% Qua].<br>
<br>
The same SB Perfed me for 996dmg standing when I was 48 and he was 49.<br>
<br>
Where Perf is concerned, SBs ownz. <br>
<br>
But if the SB misses the Perf, then gud luck SB.<br>
<br>
But yeah, trying to land the Creeping using a 2H is absurd/near impossible.<br>
<br>
To the poster who said to switch to dual weapons after 2H Perf, sorry, it won't work.<br>
<br>
Perforate [2H timer starts]<br>
Switch Weapons [hotkey]<br>
2H timer continues to tick down<br>
2H timer continues to tick down<br>
Creeping Death [1H timer starts]<br>
1H timer continues to tick down<br>
Stunning Stab.<br>
<br>
Switching weapons does not change the previous weapon-timer. That's why using Staves to Perf is not my cup'o'tea. The Timer for the Staff is still active after I switch weapons [same for 2H weapons].<br>
<br>
CD will always be a b!tch to land for 2H Critblades, but kudos to those who can. It's not easy.<br>
<br>
BTW, I'm a NS, and no, I don't b!tch about the SB who perfed me. He's good. I got more to learn. that's all. <p><fontcolor="cornflowerblue"><i>Tiejinnie<br>
