5. The points you used to raise crit skill are lost for overall damage output after your opening (even as it should be different in theory, I simply outdamage myself over time when doing la styles with 24 la, 39 sword than i do to 39 crit, 39 sword). Not to mention I apply more poisons in my la battles. Ohh did i say, that I proc more often, when using two 1h weapons?<br>
