<br>
What does this mean?  If you can do more damage in that one shot than another in a keep raid or some other insatnce you are at a great advantage because you can leave the scene of the crime faster and increase your chance of survival.<br>
<br>
It is great to jump on a keep wall and perf someone and jump of whilst your victim dies without anyone getting a target on you.  One shot is often all you get in these circumstances so doing it better is a great bonus.  This should not be overlooked.<br>
